{
  "stem": "15028.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Must have heard, the papers, even the United States, at times, if you look.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was told that the gentiles in next town, where my grandfather lived, it's only 10 kilometers away, Bosha.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And from Bosha, you-- there were the big mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You just went over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had to go over the hills to go to Bukovina, it was called.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Bosha, they had a-- the gentiles, in the evening, somehow they poured-- poured gasoline on every house-- Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- in that town-- it wasn't a village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a town, was bigger than a village-- more-- more Jewish people, and more gentile live there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they put it on fire, and it burned down completely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Every house, they burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had my uncle lived in the Bosha, and my grandfather, and an aunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were in underwater for-- they had a running water, and this is where they were living, near the water, near the river.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All the Jewish people went on the river there, and they built whatever before Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And was a-- big Thursday and Friday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Shabbos was a very, very important way of life to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father, my-- my mother, my brothers, my relatives-- in the whole, Moisei, we didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we put together food, and challahs, and bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we put on a wagon, and I and my brother-- and I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was only seven, eight years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It sticked in my mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then we went to Bosha.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We brought them the challahs and bread for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then I had an uncle in Bukovina.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was a very wealthy man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he came back-- came down after that, and he helped.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
